<h1>The best Stephen King film adaptations</h1>
<p>Welcome to TheDarkKing.com and its guide to the best Stephen King film adaptations!</p>
<h2>Reviews of Stephen King&#8217;s best film adaptations</h2>
<div class="align_left"><img src="/images/film.gif" alt="" /></div>
<p>Our reviews of the best Stephen King movie adaptations will help you to decide if it&#8217;s worth spending your time and your money watching these films. You&#8217;ll also find the main differences between Stephen King&#8217;s novels and film adapations.</p>
<h2>Visitor ratings of Stephen King&#8217;s best film adaptations</h2>
<div class="align_right"><img src="/images/rate_box.gif" alt="" /></div>
<p>Check out our visitor ratings of the best Stephen King film adaptations! The red rating bars show you which movie adaptations are the best.<br />Rate your favorite Stephen King film!</p>
<h2>Let us know what you think about Stephen King&#8217;s film adaptations</h2>
<p>Write your own comments and/or reviews about the best Stephen King movie adaptations. Let others know what&#8217;s your opinion about the movies and if they are worth to be watched!</p>
<p>We wish you a thrilling movie experience with Stephen King&#8217;s best film adaptations!</p>
<p><strong><em>TheDarkKing</em></strong></p>

